flowchart LR
    A[Git Repository or Model Change] --> B[AWS CodePipeline]
    B --> C[AWS CodeBuild Tests and Packages]
    C --> D[SageMaker Pipelines]
    D --> E[Data Processing]
    E --> F[Training and Evaluation]
    F --> G[SageMaker Model Registry]
    G --> H{Approval Gate}
    H -- Reject --> D
    H -- Approve --> I[Deploy Endpoint or Batch Workflow]
    I --> J[CloudWatch and Model Monitor]
    J --> K[Amazon EventBridge]
    K --> D
    L[CloudFormation or AWS CDK] -. provisions .-> B
    L -. provisions .-> I
